{"tid":2047527,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"申訴署促警披露《通例》標題","createTime":"2020-06-02T07:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T07:29:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"36ad65cede6f14a5f6c36dc033ae806c08fe4963","tid":2047527,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:21:23.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200602/PC2LU7E5FQBMZJVEBEALWHMXYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FPC2LU7E5FQBMZJVEBEALWHMXYI%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbQi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=bba6111e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200602%2FPC2LU7E5FQBMZJVEBEALWHMXYI%2F&h=c867020b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200602/PC2LU7E5FQBMZJVEBEALWHMXYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n申訴署促警披露《通例》標題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P63A6NR2OD4SSJFBG6REQ34ORA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP63A6NR2OD4SSJFBG6REQ34ORA.jpg&h=fb666887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方並未披露《通例》中備受關注的第29章「武力與槍械的使用」。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方屢以涉行動細節為由拒公開《警察通例》條文，令社會難以監察警隊。網媒「眾新聞」早前透過《公開資料守則》要求警方提供《警察通例》所有章節的標題遭拒，隨後向申訴專員投訴，近日獲告之投訴成立。申訴專員指通例標題只籠統交代章節主題，未包含任何具體內容，更形容警方聲稱公開標題有礙執法等的說法「實屬牽強」。<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞指去年6月20日先向警方索取《通例》第29章「武力與槍械的使用」原文遭拒；同月24日再據《公開資料守則》索取《通例》所有章節的標題，惟同樣遭拒。記者去年8月向申訴專員投訴，上月13日獲回覆指裁定投訴成立。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指有礙執法說法牽強<br />\n<br />\n申訴專員報告指，警方解釋指記者雖只要求查閱《通例》章節標題，。。。。。。。。。。，故裁定記者投訴成立，建議警方接納索取資料的要求。<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞記者收到申訴專員裁決後，再要求警方提供《通例》章節的標題，警方上周三回應稱正檢視公署報告，。。。。。。。。。。。。。公署亦無統計接獲涉及《警察通例》的投訴數字。警方回覆本報僅指正檢視申訴專員公署報告，未再交代更多細節。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛"},{"pid":"7b2fd1440f77eff189bd8b8a08a3bad8f4d5c9b7","tid":2047527,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"志雲都有講呢件事<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲 警員不可靠？全民撐國安？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2047528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2047528</a>"},{"pid":"e242b4a1c6fe2d2b0237364e78f648ad704f3642","tid":2047527,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b225149babec8320f189036e9476e863c52819bd","tid":2047527,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b2fd1440f77eff189bd8b8a08a3bad8f4d5c9b7","tid":2047527,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"志雲都有講呢件事<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲 警員不可靠？全民撐國安？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2047528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2047528</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"13:51 講警察通例"}]}